  "remarks": "LLC “Scientific And Production Association Rustecdrone” (NPO Rustecdrone) is one of the major developers and producers of unmanned aircraft systems in Russia, and supplies the Russian Ministry of Defence. Its unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), namely the RTD-4M and the UAV Inferno, are used by the Russian army in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
